{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to <strong>Ominous Stew</strong>, the chaotic 1vs1 cooking battle game that pits legendary chefs against each other in fast-paced culinary duels! Dive into the chaos in Story Mode or challenge friends in Versus Mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>The demo features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Free cooking based on nutrients</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Two restaurants battling each other in short rounds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Story Mode with 1 chapter out of 6 (Single-player and Coop)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Versus Mode (1 vs 1)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2 out of 6 playable characters with their own movement abilities and restaurants</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4 out of a dozen attacks to sabotage\u00a0the\u00a0opponent </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468420/extras/Artwork.png?t=1739211922\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468420/extras/gameconcept.png?t=1739211922\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Ominous Stew, it's restaurant vs. restaurant in thrilling 3-7 minute rounds. Move swiftly between customers to cook and serve dishes, aiming to outscore your opponent and claim culinary supremacy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468420/extras/uniquecookingmechanics.png?t=1739211922\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468420/extras/Cooking.gif?t=1739211922\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the freedom of cooking without recipes! Combine a variety of ingredients based on your customers' nutritional needs. Create unique dishes to earn points and prove your problem-solving skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468420/extras/diversecharacters.png?t=1739211922\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468420/extras/Characters.gif?t=1739211922\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock the full roster of chefs, each with their own restaurant and unique movement abilities. From simple Dashes to Table Riding - every character has a different play style with a learning curve.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468420/extras/tacticalattacks.png?t=1739211922\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468420/extras/Attacks.gif?t=1739211922\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Accumulate Foodji points by perfecting dishes, then unleash devastating attacks to sabotage your opponent. Strategic use of these powers can turn the tide of battle in your favor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468420/extras/singleplayer.png?t=1739211922\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468420/extras/Singleplayer.gif?t=1739211922\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Follow Stewy's journey from novice to culinary legend. Overcome challenges, unlock characters, attacks, bonus levels, nutrients and ingredients. Enjoy humorous dialogues and adjustable difficulty settings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468420/extras/multiplayer.png?t=1739211922\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468420/extras/Multiplayer.gif?t=1739211922\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Compete with friends in local splitscreen or through Remote Play. Select your characters, attacks, and ingredient sets to prove who\u2019s the top chef in head-to-head battles.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468420/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739211922","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468420/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739211922","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468420/7ecafb7851453898c6b67cefce4458391e5bfd3d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739211922","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3468420/7ecafb7851453898c6b67cefce4458391e5bfd3d/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739211922","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to <strong>Ominous Stew</strong>, the chaotic 1vs1 cooking battle game that pits legendary chefs against each other in fast-paced culinary duels! Dive into the chaos in Story Mode or challenge friends in Versus Mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>The demo features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Free cooking based on nutrients</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_par